<li><a href="Border_states_(American_Civil_War)" title="Border states (American Civil War)">Border states</a></li>
<li><i><a href="../Dred_Scott_v._Sandford" title="Dred Scott v. Sandford">Dred Scott v. Sandford</a></i></li>
